## Release Gate

`verify.sh` runs all of the following in sequence:

1. Python syntax check
2. Knowledge graph integrity
3. Master evaluation (`omegactl.py eval`)
4. Proof audit (`tools/proof_auditor.py`)
5. Claim audit (`tools/claim_auditor.py`)
6. Polyglot runtime validation (Rust build+test, MCP build, web build)
7. Formal invariant suite (36/36 property tests, T-1 through T-10)
8. Proof-to-implementation correspondence tests (60/60)
9. State machine tests (4/4)
10. Fuzz harnesses (75/75)
11. Lean4 machine-checked proofs (8 files, full `lake build`)

